                  "name": "aboutText",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "With over 15 years of experience in mobile development, I've had the privilege of building applications that reach millions of users. Currently leading the iOS engineering team at OKX, one of the world's largest cryptocurrency exchanges.\n\nMy journey spans from crafting early iOS apps to architecting large-scale mobile systems. I'm passionate about clean architecture, pixel-perfect UI, and mentoring engineering teams.",
